dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibexcore.coretopology

Interface IEcuInstance

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity, IIdentifiable

    public interface IEcuInstance
extends IEntity, IIdentifiable
    IEcuInstance: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    ECUInstances are used to define the ECUs used in the topology. The type of the ECU is defined by a reference to an ECU specified with the ECU resource description.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
